quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Suraj aur uski dhoop ki kasam
  91,2,Aur Chand ki kasam jabke wo uske pichey aata hai
  91,3,Aur din ki kasam jabke woh (Suraj ko) numaya kar deta hai
  91,4,Aur raat ki kasam jabke woh (suraj ko) dhank leti hai
  91,5,Aur aasman ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey qayam kiya
  91,6,Aur zameen ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey bichaya
  91,7,Aur nafs-e-Insani ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey hamwar kiya
  91,8,Phir uski badi aur uski parhezgari uss par ilham kar di
  91,9,Yaqeenan falah pa gaya woh jisne nafs ka tazkiya kiya
  91,10,Aur na-murad hua woh jisne usko daba diya
  91,11,Samood ne apni sarkashi ki bina par jhutlaya
  91,12,Jab us qaum ka sab se zyada shaqi (Badnaseeb) aadmi biphar kar utha
  91,13,To Allah ke Rasool ne un logon se kaha ke khabardar Allah ki ountni (she-camel) ko (haath na lagana) aur uske paani peene (mein maane na hona)
  91,14,Magar unhon ne uski baat ko jhuta qarar diya aur ountni ko maar dala. Aakhir-e-kaar unke gunah ke padash mein unke Rubb ne unpar aisi aafat toodi ke ek saath sab ko paywand-e-khaaq kar diya
  91,15,Aur usey (apne is fail kay) kisi burey natije ka koi khauf(darr) nahin hai